df <- as.data.frame(read.table("I13.reads_stats.txt", header = TRUE, sep = "\t", check.names = FALSE))
min_row <- ifelse(nrow(df) > 10, 10, nrow(df))
reactable(df, highlight = TRUE, bordered = TRUE, striped = TRUE, compact = TRUE, wrap = TRUE,
          filterable = TRUE, minRows = min_row, defaultColDef = colDef(minWidth = 150, align = "left"),
          theme = reactableTheme(style = list(fontFamily = "-apple-system", fontSize = "0.85em")))
